conditions to be satisfied by functions:

2. functions need to be exported i.e. they should start with upper case letter & it should be a struct
3. functions need to have two arguments & both should be exported i.e. start with uppercase & both arguments should be a struct
   i) first argument - request struct i.e. input arguments as a struct
   ii) second argument - response struct or value i.e. pointer to output
4. it must return an error
5. the fields inside struct must start with uppercase letter
